text.__SUMMARY__: Odostomia prona is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Pyramidellidae, the pyrams and their allies.
text.Distribution: This species occurs in European waters (ERMS scope).
text.Notes:
Additional information regarding this species:
Habitat: Known from seamounts and knolls
